---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro"
import graphqlSvg from "/images/graphql.svg"
import dotnetSvg from "/images/dotnet.svg"
import kubernetesSvg from "/images/kubernetes.svg"
import springSvg from "/images/spring.svg"
import nextjsSvg from "/images/nextjs.svg"

---

<BaseLayout>
  <main>
    <div class="flex gap-10 my-20 mx-14">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-end flex-1 text-right">
        <h1 class="text-6xl font-extrabold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-600 to-pink-600">
          Build different.</h1>
        <p class="mt-10 text-2xl">Often times things are pretty ugly, <br />so let's get
          <span class="font-semibold text-pink-600">architecting</span>!
        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 mt-10">
          <a href="/blog"
            class="flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-3 text-lg font-semibold bg-indigo-600 rounded-lg text-neutral-100"><span>See
              my posts</span></a>
          <a href="/about"
            class="flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-3 text-lg font-semibold border rounded-lg border-neutral-300"><span>About
              me</span></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-around flex-1 gap-5 w-[40vw]">
        <div class="flex flex-col flex-1 gap-3 p-4 font-mono text-xl text-white bg-black rounded-md">
          <p><i class="text-indigo-500 fa-solid fa-chevron-right fa-xs"></i> hxann info</p>
          <div class="flex gap-7">
            <div class="w-48">
              <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/an7/image/upload/v1656089853/blog/avatar_a8yy9u.jpg"
                class="object-cover rounded-md aspect-square" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <p>An Hoang</p>
              <a href="mailto:xuanan2001@pm.me" class="underline">xuanan2001@pm.me</a>
              <p>I do Software Engineering stuff.</p>
              <p>Coding, Architecting, criticise things engineers make.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-7">
            <i class="text-indigo-500 fa-solid fa-chevron-right fa-xs"></i> hxann links
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-start">
            <a href="/blog" class="underline">See my blog posts</a>
            <a href="/about" class="underline">About me</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/intagaming/hxann.com" class="underline">This website's source code</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="-translate-x-10 bg-pink-600 translate-y-32 h-80 w-[150vw] rotate-3 dark:bg-pink-800"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-20 py-32 text-white bg-pink-600 dark:bg-pink-800 px-60">
      <p class="text-4xl font-bold">I build software for scale. <span class="italic text-yellow-400">Easily.</span>
      </p>
      <div class="flex gap-10">
        <div class="grid flex-shrink-0 grid-flow-row grid-cols-3 gap-6 p-10 bg-gray-200 rounded-md blur-sm w-80">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
            <i class="text-orange-600 fab fa-gitlab fa-4x" />
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
            <i class="text-blue-500 fab fa-docker fa-3x" />
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
            <img src={kubernetesSvg} class="object-contain h-16" />
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
            <img src={graphqlSvg} class="object-contain h-16" />
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
            <img src={dotnetSvg} class="object-contain h-16" />
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
            <img src={springSvg} class="object-contain h-16" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-neutral-100">
            <p class="text-xl">Technologies are sometimes oversolved. Whenever it tries to do too many things, I have an
              immediate flashback of ASP.NET&apos;s <span
                class="font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-yellow-400">"ecosystem"</span>.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-5 text-xl">Using a niche framework is kind of like doing drugs. You feel cool, until you don't.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-2 mt-10">
            <p class="italic font-thin text-md">You might be interested in:</p>
            <a href="/blog/posts/about-openapi-its-tools-and-design-first-apis"
              class="flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-3 text-lg font-semibold rounded-lg bg-emerald-600 text-neutral-100"><span>About
                OpenAPI, its tools, and design-first APIs</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-20 py-48 px-60">
      <p class="text-4xl font-bold">Deep researching goes <span class="text-red-500">a long way.</span></p>
      <div class="flex w-full gap-10">
        <div class="flex-1">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-3xl font-semibold text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300">
            <p class="mt-4 ">Search for the cause.</p>
            <p>Dig to the ground.</p>
            <p class="text-amber-500 dark:text-amber-300">Every RFC is a story.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col items-start gap-2 mt-10">
            <p class="italic font-thin text-md">You might be interested in:</p>
            <a href="/blog/posts/about-the-hesitancy-in-reading-software-engineering-writings"
              class="flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-3 text-lg font-semibold rounded-lg w-[26rem] bg-rose-600 text-neutral-100"><span>About
                the hesitancy in reading Software Engineering writings</span></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center flex-1"><i
            class="text-[20em] text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-200 fas fa-book-open" /></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-16 mt-14 mb-60">
      <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold">Showcase</p>
      <div class="flex gap-3">
        <a href="https://github.com/intagaming/go-blog-backend" class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 border-2 rounded-md">
          <i class="fa-brands fa-golang"></i>
          <p>A blog backend written in Go.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/intagaming/blog2" class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 border-2 rounded-md">
          <img src={nextjsSvg} class="h-5 dark:invert" />
          <p>A Next.js blog.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/intagaming/hxann.com" class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 border-2 rounded-md">
          <i class="fa-brands fa-golang"></i>
          <p>This website's source code.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>